HYDRANS x Aqzi - Hachiwara *headphones recommended*
This was a collab with @Aqzi
[Click here ](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/hachiwara) [Or here (My SoundCloud)](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans) [Aqzi's Soundcloud](https://soundcloud.com/aquax)

Thanks for listening and make sure to support Aqzi! ~ HYDRANS
